      "content": "it's not just about a \"new path.\" the truth is, the version of me that could even care about a new path died with the work. i'm just tired of performing this version of a person who has purpose. it's exhausting to keep pretending there's a \"me\" left to find when the only thing that ever defined me was an illusion. wouldn't it be more honest to just stop the act?",
